        <briefdescription>
<para>Add a callback function to handle messages received for a specific channel. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>The callback must be registered before the sync pulse generator started when the channel is configured to synchronous mode.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
